channel.title: Christopherscape development team
channel.description:
[img]http://www.christopher.uk.com/banner13.jpg[/img] [size=15pt]Hey this is the Christopherscape Development team.
I am working on a server right now.
I want it too be the best and beat the rest.
It will be a silabsoft Server .
Carney inspired me to make this development team because i want my server too have most skills and full specials and lots more.
It will bee a bit like real rs but changed.
I can host the server 8 hours a day but anyone who could make it on 24/7 would be greatly appreciated.
I will need help making this server a grate success. This is where you will come in.
There are many OPEN SPOTS:
Testers- Psychopathic
Coders- Syrillia
Hoster-
I am using obeypk as a source. Made everywhere safe zone that is suppost too be Im making the shops in the right places. E.G armor shop in smithing place in varrock Fletching shop in catherby Pot shop in the pot shop in varrock [/size]
[size=20pt]made mage bank inside non wild[/size] [IMG]http://i181.photobucket.com/albums/x47/HELLP45/mbank.jpg[/img] [size=20pt]Skills thanks too obeypk[/size] [IMG]http://i181.photobucket.com/albums/x47/HELLP45/skills.jpg[/img] [size=20pt]Shops[/size] [IMG]http://i181.photobucket.com/albums/x47/HELLP45/shops.jpg[/img] [size=20pt]Starting place with dark wizard! skillcape one[/size] [IMG]http://i181.photobucket.com/albums/x47/HELLP45/start.jpg[/img]
